title: Integration Test Engineer
duties: Integrate software on test hardware and execute tests on that software for in-flight entertainment systems. Confirm reproducibility for bugs found and clearly dictate steps to produce them in reports. Collect and monitor logs to send diagnostic data to the software engineering team on any bugs found.

title: Data Acquisition
duties: Corrected addresses on packages as well as completed various other tasks in the small sort area. Would often be moved to other areas of the warehouse to complete duties outside of my position, such as debagging, loading and unloading trucks, and transported irregular packages.

title: Park Prep
duties: Cleaned Bathrooms, picked up litter, compacted trash and recyclables, and completed various other janitorial duties

title: Store Manager
duties: Tilled counter, managed storefront, restocked, swept floor, took out trash, looked after store. I worked alone so this was essentially a management position as I would be the only employee in the store a majority of the time.

title: Bus & Kitchen
duties: Bused tables, fried chicken, washed dishes, swept floors and parking garage, cleaned bathrooms, took out trash
